            'm.h2.3': 'Muscles — the invisible organ',
            'm.section_subt.5': 'Not just for looks. To live.',
            'm.p.1': 'Muscle mass isn\'t just aesthetics — it\'s <strong>metabolic organ, insulin buffer and longevity predictor</strong>. People with more muscle live longer, get sick less and age better. Walking and physical work help, but <strong>do not automatically build muscle</strong>, if there is no progressive loading.',
            'm.h3.10': '📉 Without training - the body breaks down slowly',
            'm.h3.11': '🚶 Walking alone is NOT enough',
            'm.h3.12': '💪 Why muscles are so important',
            'e.stat_card.1': '<div class="stat-number" style="font-size:1.6rem;">🥩</div> <div class="stat-label" data-i18n="e.hero.c1">Protein</div>',
            'e.stat_card.2': '<div class="stat-number" style="font-size:1.6rem;">🥦</div> <div class="stat-label" data-i18n="e.hero.c2">Real food</div>',
            'e.stat_card.3': '<div class="stat-number" style="font-size:1.6rem;">🚫</div> <div class="stat-label" data-i18n="e.hero.c3">No hunger</div>',
            'e.stat_box.1': '<div class="stat-number">132d</div> <div class="stat-label">protein · BGN 6.80 · without hunger</div>',
            'e.info_box.1': '<h3>Try</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">first Change only <strong>one meal</strong> today. The best start is: 3 eggs + oats + yogurt, instead of dough or jam. Don\'t diet. Make a strong breakfast.</p>',
            'e.info_box.2': '<h3 style="color:var(--red);">🏠 The take home rule</h3> <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>If it\'s not at home, you can\'t eat it in a weak moment.</strong> Environment determines behavior more than will.</p> <p style="margin-top:10px;">It\'s easier to resist <strong>once in the shop</strong>, than 20 times at home — after work, at 11:00 p.m., in front of the TV, after a bad day. Willpower is a limited resource. Don\'t spend it on things that you can solve with one shopping decision.</p> <p style="margin-top:10px; color:var(--muted);">You don\'t buy chips → you don\'t eat chips. You buy walnuts → you eat walnuts. So simple.</p> <div class="stat-pills mt-16"> <span class="stat-pill green">The environment &gt; will</span> <span class="stat-pill green">1 solution in store = 20 wins at home</span> <span class="stat-pill amber">Garbage is designed to be addictive</span> </div>',
            'e.info_box.3': '<h3>💊 Do you want to speed up the results?</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">Once the basics are in order—food, sleep, exercise—see which supplements are actually proven and how to take them.</p> <a class="btn btn-green" href="supplements.html" style="margin-top:16px; display:inline-block;">See add-ons →</a> ',
            'e.meal_card.1': '<div class="meal-label">Breakfast</div> <strong>3 eggs + oatmeal with banana</strong> <div class="meal-protein">~26g protein · ~1.80 BGN</div>',
            'e.meal_card.2': '<div class="meal-label">Lunch</div> <strong>Chicken legs + rice + salad</strong> <div class="meal-protein">~52g protein · ~3.20 BGN</div>',
            'e.meal_card.3': '<div class="meal-label">Dinner</div> <strong>Lentil stew + yogurt</strong> <div class="meal-protein">~38g protein · ~1.80 BGN</div>',
            'e.cta_section.1': '<h2>Eat right.<br/><em class="green">Pay less.</em></h2> <p style="color:#888; margin-bottom:24px;">See real prices this week — with in-store promotions.</p> <a class="btn btn-green" href="start.html">Get the 7 day plan →</a> ',
            'e.h3.1': '🥦 Real food (the 5 ingredient rule)',
            'e.h3.2': '💧 Water - at least 2 liters per day',
            'e.h3.3': '🍭 Sugar is the silent killer',
            'e.h3.4': '📈 Insulin sensitivity — why it matters',
            'e.h2.1': 'Food tier list',
            'e.section_subt.1': 'Cheap, accessible, packed with nutrients',
            'e.food_group.1': '🥩 Proteins',
            'e.food_group.4': '🥜 Fats',
            'e.food_group.5': '🍚 Carbs',
            'e.food_group.legend': '📌 Legend',
            'e.tier.protein': '<p>Not every protein is equally good. Look at protein density, satiety, processing, and whether you can eat it often without blowing your budget.</p>',
            'e.tier.carbs': '<p>Carbs are not the enemy. What matters is whether they give stable energy and satiety, or push you into hunger and sleepiness.</p>',
            'e.tier.fats': '<p>Fats are not just calories. They affect hormones, satiety, and recovery. But there is a huge difference between olive oil and fried junk.</p>',
            'e.tier.legend': '<p>S tier = strongest base. A tier = very good. B tier = okay, but not optimal. F tier = as rare as possible.</p>',
            'e.h3.5': '🥚 Eggs — 9/10',
