            's.info_box.1': '<h3>Try</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">first Don\'t think about the whole 7 days. Open <strong>Day 1</strong> and fulfilled only him. The best plan is the one you start today, not the one that sounds perfect.</p>',
            's.info_box.2': '<h3>Bad day? Make the minimum</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">If the day goes wrong, don\'t write it all off. Just do this:</p> <p style="margin-top:8px;">• <strong>10 minutes walk</strong></p> <p>• <strong>1 protein meal</strong>— eggs, yogurt, chicken, lentils, cottage cheese</p> <p>• <strong>30 minutes without phone before sleep</strong></p> <p style="margin-top:8px; color:var(--muted);">That counts again. Don\'t wait for Monday. Continue from the next action.</p>',
            's.info_box.3': '<h3 style="color:#7F77DD;">3 options:</h3> <p data-i18n-html="s.after.opt1" style="margin-top:12px;"><strong>1. Repeat</strong>— did the same week again. You already know how.</p> <p data-i18n-html="s.after.opt2"><strong>2. Add something</strong>— more reps, more steps, new recipe.</p> <p data-i18n-html="s.after.opt3"><strong>3. Open Smart Food</strong> — <a href="smart-food.html">see the offers and shop smarter</a>.</p>',
            's.info_box.4': '<p style="font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.7; margin:0 0 16px;">Changing for the better is very important, but sometimes it can be challenging!<br/>If you need advice or motivation, contact me.</p> <a href="mailto:ivvmilev@gmail.com" style="color:#7F77DD; font-weight:600; font-size:1rem; text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid #7F77DD;">ivvmilev@gmail.com</a> ',
            's.info_box.5': '<h3>No drama. Get back.</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;"><strong>Missed 1 day?</strong> Continue tomorrow.</p> <p><strong>Missed 3 days?</strong> Go back to Day 1.</p> <p><strong>Missed a week?</strong> Go into "Minimum" mode for 2 days and catch the rhythm again.</p> <p style="margin-top:12px; color:var(--muted);">No punishment. No starving. No “starting Monday.” The next good action is enough.</p>',
            's.info_box.6': '<h3>You don’t need fancy.</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">With this you have a few days of normal food, solid protein, and zero unnecessary theory.</p> <p style="margin-top:12px;"><a href="smart-food.html" style="color:#7F77DD; font-weight:600;">Want real offers and smarter shopping? See Smart Food →</a></p>',
