            's.span.1': '0 of 6 completed',
            'sup.info_box.1': '<h3 style="color:var(--amber);">⚠️ Before additions - check if:</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">✓ You eat 1.6g+ protein/kg · ✓ You sleep 7–9 hours · ✓ You exercise 150 min/week · ✓ You drink 2l+ water</p> <p style="margin-top:8px; color:var(--muted);">If not, the supplements are useless. Fix the foundation first.</p>',
            'sup.info_box.2': '<h3>Try</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">first Don\'t buy 5 things. Make sure you\'re sleeping, eating protein, and moving. If the base is OK, start with <strong>only one</strong> a supplement that really makes sense for you.</p>',
            'sup.info_box.3': '<h3>Total: ~48 BGN/month</h3> <p style="margin-top:8px;">For less than the price of a month\'s fitness membership, you get 4 of the most well-researched health interventions.</p>',
            'sup.timeline.1': '<div class="timeline-item"> <div class="timeline-label">Step 1</div> <h3>Fix the base</h3> <p>Eating, sleeping, moving. Without them, add-ons are a waste of money.</p> </div> <div class="timeline-item"> <div class="timeline-label">Step 2</div> <h3>Vitamin D3 + K2 and Magnesium</h3> <p>Almost everyone is deficient. The effect is quick and clear — better sleep, more energy, better mood.</p> <div class="stat-pills"> <span class="stat-pill green">~18 BGN/month</span> </div> </div> <div class="timeline-item"> <div class="timeline-label">Step 3</div> <h3>Omega-3</h3> <p>If you don\'t eat oily fish regularly — add quality fish fatty oil.</p> <div class="stat-pills"> <span class="stat-pill green">~15 BGN/month</span> </div> </div> <div class="timeline-item"> <div class="timeline-label">Step 4</div> <h3>Creatine</h3> <p>When training is regular. The effect accumulates - after 4 weeks you will feel a clear difference.</p> <div class="stat-pills"> <span class="stat-pill green">~15 BGN/month</span> </div> </div>',
            'sup.cta_section.1': '<h2>The foundation first.<br/><em class="green">Then supplements.</em></h2> <p style="color:#888; max-width:480px; margin:0 auto 24px;">If you haven\'t — see the 7-day plan to get started.</p> <a class="btn btn-green" href="start.html">See the 7-day plan →</a> ',
